data.description: Well cared for custom home in exclusive Quail Run on almost 3/4 acre corner lot with a huge front porch; relax and enjoy country living close to the city & bases! Retired vet owner reduced price to sell & for upgrades/any repairs needed! Downsizing so appliances stay(except fridge) furniture also possible. Split, open floor plan, guest suite, island kitchen w/gas stove, office, enclosed patio & new roof in 2021! Tray ceilings, large utility room w/sink & workbench in garage. Great neighborhood w/low cost HOA & all comparable sized lots app 6 miles to 410 and 1604.
